    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the maze with friends or players worldwide and see who is the ultimate seeker or the most elusive hider. Learn the maze and find the best hiding spots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently, there is only one game mode where a survivor joins the hunters when caught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365380/extras/96127baf31f5e9f5319f213feda272e9.poster.avif?t=1737936518\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365380/extras/96127baf31f5e9f5319f213feda272e9.webm?t=1737936518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365380/extras/96127baf31f5e9f5319f213feda272e9.mp4?t=1737936518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both hiders and seekers can dash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365380/extras/99883a40ff74269aab80310dd7df2bd1.poster.avif?t=1737936518\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365380/extras/99883a40ff74269aab80310dd7df2bd1.webm?t=1737936518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365380/extras/99883a40ff74269aab80310dd7df2bd1.mp4?t=1737936518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hider has two additional abilities: silent footsteps and invisibility. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365380/extras/fb7baebba7e4725140254b432a92fcbb.poster.avif?t=1737936518\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365380/extras/fb7baebba7e4725140254b432a92fcbb.webm?t=1737936518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365380/extras/fb7baebba7e4725140254b432a92fcbb.mp4?t=1737936518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunters run faster but have just one ability which is search. Target a region on the map to see how many, if any, hiders are there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your character with Ready Player Me avatar creator.</p>",
